text: Hi NAMESLOTU.
How are you today?
"i am good, how are you?"

How can I help you today?

Let me help you with that.
"Can you verify your first and last name, please?"
NAMESLOTU
And can I get your billing address so that I can look up the order number
ADDRSLOT
One moment while I look up your order...
no worries

sure

What is the credit card number of the card used?
do you not have that card number on the system?
Yes.
I need to verify the information here to be sure it was the correct card.
it's the card ending in 8166 I don't feel comfortable giving away my full card number

Do you mind giving me the expiration date of the card?

This is NAMESLOTA from Amazon Customer Service.
I find why your package has not been received

Yes.
I have your order summary here and it was flagged for incorrect payment information.

I need the number and exp date on card to expedite the shipping to you

"Why do you need my expiration date, NAMESLOTA?"
